\f0\pard Introduction to the sample document.\par
This RTF fixture exercises the flat-paragraph extractor.\par
RTF has no semantic heading tags, so every block is a paragraph.\par
Each paragraph is separated by a paragraph-break control word.\par
The byte-identity invariant must hold for every emitted block.\par}
